Text: Description:nnAppDelete 3.1.2 by appleXsnn============================nnAppDelete is an uninstaller for Macs that will remove not only Applications but also Widgets, Preference Panes, Plugins and Screensavers along with their associated files.  Without AppDelete these associated items will be left behind to take up space and potentially cause issues.  For a proper uninstall don?t just delete but be sure to AppDelete!
